pages.title: Bigeye Trevally
pages.text: Other more detailed anatomical features also set the species apart from other members of Caranx.$(br2)The species is known to grow to a length of 120 cm and 18 kg.$(br2)The fish is known to move from a more crustacean dominated diet as a juvenile to a nearly completely fish dominated diet as an adult.
